# Doom2D Forever

Modern C++ rewrite of Doom2D.

## Quick start (Windows)

```bat
build.bat
run_game.bat
run_engine.bat
```

- `run_game.bat` — full game (`d2df.exe`)
- `run_engine.bat` — engine playground (`d2df_engine.exe`), map + movement only

Requires: CMake 3.25+, MSVC 2022, vcpkg (`VCPKG_ROOT` or `C:\vcpkg`).

Runtime assets: `assets/content/` (maps, textures, sounds).

See [BUILD.md](BUILD.md) and [docs/](docs/) for details.
